Break Cinnamon Crisp(R) into bite-size pieces. Spread Cinnamon Crisp(R) pieces, raisins, nuts, and sunflower seeds on large greased jelly roll pan, about 15 x 10 inches. In small saucepan melt butter with honey; drizzle over graham mixture. Bake in preheated 250 degrees F oven 45 minutes. Allow to cool in pan. Loosen mixture with metal spatula. Store in airtight container or jar.